#: src/Admin/ModulesPage.php:1096
msgid ""
"Continuous, passive monitoring of front-end fatal errors, the checkout "
"failure rate, and sales anomalies (\"traffic but no orders\"). Sends email "
"or webhook alerts. Checks run every 5 minutes and never place synthetic "
"orders."
msgstr ""
